io.wcm.caravan.rhyme.api

Interface RhymeBuilder


  • @ProviderType
public interface RhymeBuilder
    A builder to configure and create a Rhyme instance to be used throughout the lifecycle of the incoming request.

      • withRhymeDocsSupport

        RhymeBuilder withRhymeDocsSupport(RhymeDocsSupport rhymeDocsSupport)
        Enable generation of curie links (to HTML documentation generated with the rhyme-docs-maven-plugin) when rendering HalResponses with Rhyme.renderResponse(io.wcm.caravan.rhyme.api.resources.LinkableResource). If you call this method, you also have to ensure that you actually serve the generated HTML files using RhymeDocsSupport.loadGeneratedHtml(RhymeDocsSupport, String)
        Parameters:
        rhymeDocsSupport - the SPI instance that handles loading of the generated HTML
        Returns:
        this
